Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:46.80,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}喂  能听到吗{\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.36,0:01:49.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}与你一起极限战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:52.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}狰狞无比的凄惨之战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:54.65,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}爱总是无法无天的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.25,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}仅属于我的放荡之战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:01.30,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那句再见  无法说出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:04.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我真是没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:06.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我不明白  我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:08.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}搞不明白自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:14.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}这份心情无法释怀  无法割舍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:19.59,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}越是想着不可以  就陷得越深
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:24.76,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}变得连自己都开始怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:28.36,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不如相信它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:32.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不管会失去什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:35.49,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}都决定要伴随在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:36.10,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:39.05,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:41.77,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}就算到了明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:44.25,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I want you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:46.97,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}命运要我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:49.59,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:52.10,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}要我止步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:54.54,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I need you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:56.83,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}这理由却还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:03:01.65,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我可为你抛弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:02.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}与你一起极限战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:07.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}狰狞无比的凄惨之战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:09.88,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}爱总是无法无天的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:12.54,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}仅属于我的放荡之战
